  是否运行以下命令？

  原因：this is a test reason such as one that would be produced by the model

  $ echo hello world

› 1. 是，继续 (y)
  2. 是，且不再询问以 `echo hello world` 开头的命令 (p)
  3. 否，告诉 Codex 换个做法 (esc)

  Press enter 确认或 esc 取消
